      • getAccessManager

        public static <T extends CycAccessSession> CycAccessManager<T> getAccessManager()
        Returns an implementation of CycAccessManager. It will return the first implementation it finds which has been registered per ServiceLoader. If one has not been specified, it will fall back on the default implementation.
        Returns:
        an object which implements CycAccessManager.
